cello.alt.servlet.script
Class DirectoryScriptLoader

java.lang.Object
  cello.alt.servlet.script.ScriptLoader
      cello.alt.servlet.script.DirectoryScriptLoader

public class DirectoryScriptLoader
extends ScriptLoader

This class provides a standard filesystem directory based ScriptLoader. That is, it looks for files in its path and returns new FileResource objects.

Author:
Marcello
